            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Project 1</h2>
                <p>Some description of the project. This card has a nice hover effect that elevates it slightly and adds depth with shadow.</p>
                <div class="card-link">
                    <a href="#">View project →</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project Card 2 -->
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="public/Blue ABstract Brain Technology Logo (1).png" alt="Project 2" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Blog</h2>
                <p>I write blogs when I feel like it. Most of it is relevant to what I do daily, so it's also an another perspective on my work.</p>
